trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection> provides programmatic access to check whether an identity associated with a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRole> has been added to a <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> or <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WebServiceInputActivity>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection> fornece acesso programático para verificar se uma identidade associado com um <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRole> foi adicionado a um <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.HandleExternalEventActivity> ou <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.WebServiceInputActivity>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the identity for which to search.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém a identidade que deseja pesquisar.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" /> contains the specified identity.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" /> contém a identidade especificada.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" /> contains the identity; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Activities.WorkflowRoleCollection" /> contiver a identidade, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.
